<item>
            <title>[PIG-4315] MergeJoin or Split followed by order by gives NPE in Tez</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-4315</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;TestHBaseStorage.testMergeJoin() fails. connectingLR is null in CombinerOptimizer and throws NPE in &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;from.plan.getOperator(connectingLR.getOperatorKey())
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;When splitting DAGs and doing moveTree TezCompilerUtil.connect() overwrites the output key of sampler LocalRearrange to the partitioner vertex.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Split followed by orderby also had issues using the same TezCompilerUtil.connect()  method.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
